{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873780/extras/BannerImage_StoreDescript.png?t=1729756299\" /><strong>NecroFarm</strong> is part farming and part tower defense. Strategically plant crops and turn them into your unholy minions! Defend your farm against waves of enemies. Your minions patrol and fight monsters on their own but you can also command them to attack target enemies. How many waves of enemies can you survive? How much gold can you accumulate from selling crops? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Reap and Raise!</strong> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873780/extras/SentreeSummon.gif?t=1729756299\" /></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Necromancer-inspired gameplay. Summon and command unholy crop minions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gain new minions and grow your army size.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plant crops and harvest them to sell or turn them into minions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wave-based horde survival with escalating difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Atmospheric and fun spooky environments!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Grow Them, Raise Them!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873780/extras/GrowRaise2.gif?t=1729756299\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Minions follow your command!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1873780/extras/Command2.gif?t=1729756299\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Graveyard Shift","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/imag